The bundled Six Sigma study content is a translated and structured learning edition derived from `CSSC Lean Six Sigma Black Belt Certification Training Manual.pdf`, which is listed as a free PDF on the CSSC training-materials page: https://www.sixsigmacouncil.org/six-sigma-training-material/

The original manual content remains owned by its respective rights holder. This project does not claim ownership of the original manual text, figures, tables, logos, or course material.

